overview.en: Flash payment is a global payment platform based on consensus and stable currency, with points as SF. The main business of the platform includes currency exchange, currency exchange, international transfer, international payment, financial management, lending and games
overview.zh: 闪付是以共识稳定币为基础的全球支付平台，积分为SF，平台主要业务包括货币兑换币币兑换、国际转账、国际支付、理财、借贷、游戏等
